        <li><strong>fetchAdResults</strong> â€” retrieves impressions and clicks for completed campaigns</li>
        <li><strong>blogCreation</strong> â€” generates blog posts in Ghost CMS with venue recommendations, meta descriptions, and tags</li>
      </ul>

