    <section>
      <h2>5. Social Shoutout Campaigns</h2>
      <p>
        In addition to the three self-service modules, Prime includes quarterly social media shoutout campaigns. These are managed ad hoc by the Growth team (no API endpoint) and involve:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>A pre-planned database of campaign slots across the year</li>
        <li>Filming sessions with venues, with content locked 2 weeks before end of quarter</li>
        <li>Scheduling based on city/location validation</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        These are not part of the self-service UI and remain a manual, Growth-led process.
      </p>
    </section>

